# Normalize to LF in the repo (papercut: mixed CRLF/LF broke patch scripts and
# spammed warnings on every commit). Editors/tools get LF on checkout too.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.svg text
*.mp3 binary
*.ogg binary
*.wav binary
*.flac binary
*.m4a binary
*.ico binary
*.woff2 binary
